title: How Jenna Compono Became the Barbie Beast of ‘The Challenge’ | Death Taxes, and Bananas
description:
Jenna Compono joins Johnny to talk about her recent nuptials, becoming a mother, and how she established herself as the Barbie Beast on ‘The Challenge’ with three finals under her belt and an elimination record to be envied.
Host: Johnny Bananas
Guest: Jenna Compono
Producer: Sasha Ashall
